OL,6,FOn the incident which took place on
OL,7,FNovember 3 at Parliament's Derby Gate,
OL,8,Fhe said: "During the incident I spoke
OL,9,Fto the complainant in a manner that
OL,10,Fwas totally unacceptable and which
OL,11,Fincluded swearing and other language
OL,12,Fthat goes against the House of Commons
OL,13,Fbullying and harassment policy.
OL,15,F"I would like to apologies to the
OL,16,Fcomplainant and to this House for my
OL,17,Fbehaviour.
OL,19,F"Our security staff do an incredible
OL,20,Fjob and should always be treated with
OL,21,Fthe utmost of respect.
