OL,6,F"The standards of an MP's behaviour
OL,7,Fmust always be at a higher standard.
OL,9,F"I give you and this House my firm
OL,10,Fassurance that I've learned
OL,11,Fsignificant lessons through this
OL,12,Fprocess, and a firm undertaking that
OL,13,Fsuch behaviour on my part will never
OL,14,Fhappen again."
